<button *ngIf="switch && htmlInputElement.value" matSuffix mat-icon-button (click)="switchVisibility()">

</button>
<button *ngIf="!switch && htmlInputElement.value" matSuffix mat-icon-button (click)="switchVisibility()">

</button>
